<p>'Like, planning and who can and can't come, and who's involved and who's not involved - that s*** is annoying to me. And it's not becoming what Malika wants it to be, it's becoming what everyone else wants it to be.'</p>

<p>After hanging up on them, Kardashian and Haqq called her back to discover she was crying.    </p>

